        }
      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Proposal\n\nRecommended first-class planning nodes:\n- Goal\n- Task\n- Decision\n- Open Question\n- Constraint\n- Risk\n\nRecommended relational-first concept:\n- Dependency\n\nRecommended structured attachment concept:\n- Acceptance Criteria\n\nThis proposal favors node types where lifecycle, provenance, and prompt relevance matter most.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
