        }
      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Recommended First Wave\n\nImplement these as first-class planning node types first:\n\n1. Goal\n2. Task\n3. Decision\n4. Open Question\n5. Constraint\n6. Risk\n\nWhy:\n- each has distinct semantics\n- each benefits from explicit lifecycle or status\n- each adds value beyond plain markdown\n- each is likely to matter in prompting and review",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
