      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Suggested Next Step\n\nTurn the first-wave proposal into concrete node schemas:\n- required fields\n- optional fields\n- lifecycle/status fields\n- relationship rules\n- prompt/export behavior\n\nThat gives Grok, Claude, and me one clean target to compare instead of arguing at pure concept level.",
